  "title": "Admin & Accounts Officer (Ubi / Automotive industries) [EL]",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Working hours: 5 days + 1 half day Sat per month</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>80% Admin + 20% Accounts</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Car Registration</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Review car registration folder for payment status, required documentation, approvals, and remarks</li>\n  <li>Input car registration details via LTA Link</li>\n  <li>Maintain and update the registration folder</li>\n  <li>Process refund cheques, if applicable</li>\n  <li>Place number plate orders with Europlate Design</li>\n  <li>Submit IU commissioning requests to Indecco</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Accounts / Other Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Generate and issue invoices</li>\n  <li>Prepare month-end reports, including showroom inventory, car financing analysis, and sales performance analysis</li>\n  <li>Prepare and post sub-ledger journals for deposit transfers and visa waivers</li>\n  <li>Handle any additional tasks as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
